{"id":2037,"date":"2022-12-06T14:34:10","date_gmt":"2022-12-06T05:34:10","guid":{"rendered":"https://blogbooks.net/?p=2037"},"modified":"2022-12-06T14:34:11","modified_gmt":"2022-12-06T05:34:11","slug":"2037","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/2037/","title":{"rendered":"学校のChromeBookに拡張機能を追加する方法。"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">はじめまして！ここあと言います。<br>早速ですが、「学校のChromeBookに拡張機能を入れたいなー」なんて思ったことないですか？<br>この記事を見ている人なら、思ったことがあると思います。<br>そこで、今回は&#8221;<strong>学校のChromeBookに拡張機能を追加する方法</strong>&#8220;を紹介していきたいと思います。<br><br>　<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">〜必要なもの</span>〜</strong><br>・<strong>Windowsのパソコン</strong><br>・<strong>スマホ</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>～やり方～</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>まずはWindowsのChromeで学校のアカウントにログインして「同期」をします</strong>。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2046\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/2037/attachment/image-41/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image.png\" data-orig-size=\"1022,680\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-300x200.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2046\" width=\"448\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image.png 1022w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-300x200.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-768x511.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-medium-font-size\"><strong>続いて他の端末（スマートフォンなど）で学校のアカウントにログインし、</strong><br><strong>パスワードを変更してください。</strong><br>&#x1f50d;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/41078?hl=ja&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\" target=\"_blank\">Googleのパスワードを変更する方法</a><br><strong>パスワードを変更が完了したらWindowsのChrome戻り、左上が、一時停止になるはずです。</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"464\" height=\"76\" data-attachment-id=\"2047\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/2037/attachment/image-1-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1.png\" data-orig-size=\"464,76\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1-300x49.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2047\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1.png 464w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-1-300x49.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 464px) 100vw, 464px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>一時停止のマークが確認出来たらWebStoreを開きましょう！<br>&#x1f50d; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions?hl=ja\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions?hl=ja\" target=\"_blank\">WebStoreURL</a></strong><br><strong>そうして、以下の画面が開かれたら成功です！</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2052\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/2037/attachment/image-2-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2.png\" data-orig-size=\"1358,619\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-300x137.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-1024x467.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-1024x467.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2052\" width=\"530\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-1024x467.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-300x137.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2-768x350.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-2.png 1358w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>目的の拡張機能を入れることができたらWindowsのChromeで学校のアカウントにログインしましょう</strong>。<br><strong>ここまで読んでいただきありがとうございました。</strong></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"はじめまして！ここあと言います。早速ですが、「学校のChromeBookに拡張機能を入れたいなー」な&#8230;","protected":false},"author":20,"featured_media":2042,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2,6],"tags":[8,9,10,11,14,21],"class_list":["post-2037","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chromebook","category-6","tag-chrome","tag-chromebook","tag-10","tag-11","tag-14","tag-21"],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/nuke.png","jetpack_shortlink":"https://wp.me/s5wAvD-2037","nishiki_blocks_pro":{"display_name":"ここあ","author_link":"https://blogbooks.net/written-by/5950b5e85be26fcc76f3976a03a17780adc3e40e/","featured_image":"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/nuke.png","category":[{"name":"chromebook","link":"https://blogbooks.net/category/chromebook/","id":2},{"name":"ブロック回避","link":"https://blogbooks.net/category/chromebook/%e3%83%96%e3%83%ad%e3%83%83%e3%82%af%e5%9b%9e%e9%81%bf/","id":6}],"excerpt":"はじめまして！ここあと言います。早速ですが、「学校のChromeBookに拡張機能を入れたいなー」な...","terms":[{"term_id":2,"name":"chromebook","slug":"chromebook","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":2,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":147,"filter":"raw"},{"term_id":6,"name":"ブロック回避","slug":"%e3%83%96%e3%83%ad%e3%83%83%e3%82%af%e5%9b%9e%e9%81%bf","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":6,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":2,"count":116,"filter":"raw"},{"term_id":8,"name":"chrome","slug":"chrome","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":8,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":118,"filter":"raw"},{"term_id":9,"name":"chromebook","slug":"chromebook","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":9,"taxonomy":"post_tag",